title: Top 10 RB Rankings, Beer Draft, James Conner Interview (Football 7/4)
description:
Will Brinson and Heath Cummings rank the top 10 running backs in the NFL and then do a draft for best summer beers. Will then interviews Steelers running back James Conner. NOTE: This was recorded before it was announced Ezekiel Elliott wouldn't be suspended.
